Pull Nagios Docker Image
Run in PowerShell:
docker pull jasonrivers/nagios:latest


Run the Nagios Container
Run the exact command from your document:
docker run --name nagiosdemo -p 8888:80 jasonrivers/nagios:latest

To keep it running in background, stop it and restart detached:
docker stop nagiosdemo
docker rm nagiosdemo
docker run -d --name nagiosdemo -p 8888:80 jasonrivers/nagios:latest


Access the Nagios Dashboard
Open your browser:
http://localhost:8888
Login with:
username: nagiosadmin
password: nagios


